1.en: The cost of a full-time MBA programme, especially from those schools at the top end of the rankings, remains significant.
1.cn: 全日制MBA课程，特别是在顶级商学院，花费依然很高。

2.en: The character which when preceded by an escape character represents the word-end boundary assertion.
2.cn: 前跟转义字符用于判断单词结束边界的字符。

3.en: In the end, I decided to take her out to play some day we dined together, to talk about the heart and another slip of the ice.
3.cn: 终于，我决定带她出去玩一下，那天我们一起吃了饭，谈了心，又一起溜了冰。

1.en: I can end Dunbar's campaign. We can end it today.
1.cn: 我可以终结邓巴的竞选，今天就结束掉。

3.en: Look it's the end of the date, I'm standing there.
3.cn: 约会结束了，我站在那里。

4.en: And end this war before it ever begins.
4.cn: 从而，在灭绝变种人开始前，结束这场战争。

5.en: Please hold all questions till the end of the presentation.
5.cn: 请等演讲结束后再提问。

6.en: And then Daddy came and rescued her. The end.
6.cn: 最后是爸爸把他救出来。故事结束了。

7.en: They shot Nick Fury. And it won't end there.
7.cn: 他们刺杀了尼克弗瑞，事情没有到此结束。

8.en: And when this rock disappears, that Truce will end.
8.cn: 等和平岩消失的时候，休战期也就结束了。

9.en: Thank you, that's the end of my amazingly impossible circus.
9.cn: 谢谢，我的神奇的不可能的马戏团表演要结束了。

10.en: That's the end. Goodbye children. Happy Christmas. Happy Christmas everybody.
10.cn: 结束了孩子们，圣诞快乐！祝大家圣诞节快乐！

11.en: It's a relationship that is about to end and when this will end you will never see this person again.
11.cn: 这段关系就要结束了结束之后，你再也不会和这个人见面。

12.en: Of course, the end of our combat mission in Afghanistan doesn't mean the end of challenges to our security.
12.cn: 当然，我们在阿富汗战斗任务的结束，并不意味着对我们安全挑战的结束。

13.en: I'm dedicating my life to your deaths. This war will not end.
13.cn: 我会穷尽一生找你索命，这场战争不会结束。

14.en: The end of freshman year, I kind of dated the swim team captain.
14.cn: 一年级快结束那年，我跟游泳队队长约过会。

15.en: And you don't think that person has the right to end his or her life?
15.cn: 你不认为这样的人有权利结束自己的生命吗？

16.en: Come on, I didn't want anyone to feel bad at the end of the game.
16.cn: 拜托，我不想让任何人在游戏结束的时候伤心啊。

17.en: Absolem? Why are you upside down? I've come to the end of this life.
17.cn: 亚伯索伦？你怎么挂在那里？我的生命就快结束了。

18.en: May her powers signify the end of tyranny and the beginning of a new era.
18.cn: 愿她的力量意味着暴政的结束和一个新时代的开启。

19.en: I did not see that common twist ending. My stories never end like that.
19.cn: 没有出人意料的结局, 我的故事从来不会这样结束。
